Detailed Description

This message is sent to the active application whenever a user releases a key. m_key_code: contains the key code of the key released m_duration: contains the duration of the key press. Duration is measured by AXE_TICKS_PER_SECOND AXE_LONG_KEY_PRESS_DURATION and AXE_VERY_LONG_KEY_PRESS_DURATION define the time span of a long key or very long key press in AXE_TICKS_PER_SECOND
